tools.description:
Query the current live/offline status of a channel.

Args:
    channel_id (str): The unique identifier of the channel.

Returns:
    dict: 
        On success:
            {
                "success": True,
                "data": {
                    "channel_id": str,
                    "current_status": str  # "live" or "offline"
                }
            }
        On failure:
            {
                "success": False,
                "error": str
            }

Constraints:
    - channel_id must exist in the system.
